[FILE:229:descriptions/desc.single]
KSBA = rot13(digit_to_letter(x509)) to be pronounced as Kasbah

KSBA is a library to make X.509 certificates as well as the CMS easily
accessible by other applications.  Both specifications are building
blocks of S/MIME and TLS.


